
                                                        +-------+
                                                        |  .BI  |
                                                        +-------+

BOLD ITALIC overstrikes an input line with itself and underscores
it for a boldface italic effect.

     +-------+---------------------------------------------+
     |       |                                             |
     |  .BI  |    <<.U+>1<.U->|n|ON|OFF|line>                        |<.NORMAL>
     |       |                                             |
     +-------+---------------------------------------------+

The operands are identical to those for the .BD control word.

<.U+>EXAMPLES<.NORMAL>
(1) This is
    .BI Bold Italic text
    and this
    .BI ON;is more Bold Italic
    output text.
    .BI OFF
    .BI .CE BOLD ITALIC END
    produces:   This  is <.B+><.U+>Bold Italic text<.U->  <.B-><.U->and this <.B+><.U+>is  more Bold<.NORMAL>
    <.B+><.U+>Italic output text<.U->.<.NORMAL>
                           <.B+><.U+>BOLD ITALIC END<.NORMAL>

